        <div class="panel-heading">
            <a href="/markdown.html">Markdown Basics</a>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
        <h1 id="markdown">Markdown</h1>
<p>Markdown is a popular text format for editing files. It is often used to produce well formatted web content. It is used extensively by GitHub, Reddit, Stack Overflow, and many others. </p>
<p>One of the easiest ways to become familiar with Markdown is to <a href="https://stackedit.io">give it a try</a>!</p>
<h2 id="text-formatting">Text formatting</h2>
<h3 id="bold-italics-lists">Bold, italics, lists</h3>
<div class="codehilite"><pre>*This is italic*

**This is bold**

This sentence has **bold**, *italics*, and ***bold-italics***

* This is a list item
* So is this
    * And this is a sublist item

Numbered lists are</pre></div>
        <a href="/markdown.html" class="btn btn-default">...</a>
        </div>
    </div>

