<h1 id="overview">Overview</h1>
<p>Adding pages to your PyKwiki consists of two main pieces.</p>
<ol>
<li>Some way to get your content to a server.</li>
<li>Some way to run <code>pykwiki cache</code> to cache your content.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="things-to-know">Things to know</h2>
<p>Technical knowledge: </p>
<ol>
<li>A basic understand of <a href="/markdown.html">Markdown</a>.</li>
<li>A basic understanding of the <a href="http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#Introduction">YAML</a></li></ol>
        <a href="/authoring.html" class="btn btn-default">...</a>
